## function flow_step_list_batch | doc="flow_step.list — list flow_step rows for one flow, joined LEFT to role for the optional requires_role name. Sorted by (sort_order, label, id)." | path="functions/flow_step_list_batch.sql"
## function flow_step_list_for_card_batch | doc="flow_step.list_for_card — read-side affordance API: walk parent_card_id (RECURSIVE depth<16) to find the enclosing project, then list every flow_step the card may currently fire — one row per (flow, attribute_def, from_card_id=card's value) match — pre-joined with from/to titles+phases, optional requires_role name, and a per-actor allowed bit (system bypass + project-or-global scope check)." | path="functions/flow_step_list_for_card_batch.sql"
## function card_type_select_batch | doc="card_type.select — list every card_type row (global reference data; no per-input filter today). One input → one result row; same snapshot replicated per input." | path="functions/card_type_select_batch.sql"
